FHEM TALKTOME AND TALKTOUSER last changes:
2016-07-06
 - Added possibility to load a complete directory with rivescript files (ending .rs or .rive) through attribute rsbraindir
 - Fixed logging of helper functions

2016-07-03
 - Added call to perl - At this point it is an alpha release, no guarantee that this works!
 - Fixed the log functions. To debug the "<call>" statements, you need to set the verbose level on global

2016-06-30
 - Removed default attributes icon, group and rsbrainfile
 - Fixed the possibility to disable the module TALKTOME
 - Added rspunctuation as attribute to enable other special characters
 
2016-06-21
 - Initial Upload of the TALKTO modules